抬緊 定 奮戰中，記者影到登上報嘅話，形象可以感染到中間派、保守嘅人、冇出嘅人 同埋 贏到輿論。<br />\n<br />\n討論，勿屌。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:29:31.000Z","msg":"頭帶有條鐵用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係屌你，係覺得好笑"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"補充:103萬個人頭都無用，就算有幾萬個戴頭帶會有咩作用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:47:33.000Z","msg":"你想用條頭帶令政府撤回 定係 想條頭帶可以擋子彈？<br />\n形象感染呀，針對我講嗰班人。<br />\n當然你唔好expect功效十足，但相比起國旗有用。<br />\n<br />\n硬有硬，軟有軟。唔好一味諗點直接攻政府，有啲間接嘅手法都要用。俾你成萬勇士做到野，但出面個個香港人當你暴徒搗亂，有咩用？政府出黎開個記招 然後出面所有人都唔想同你同隊，變相沉默支持政府。俾人地理解你嘅行動、明白你嘅激動，即使最後人地唔出黎支持你 都唔會出聲屌你啦。"},{"pid":"67c02fbdac6aa0999f7c94e58868b5aa6cdad770","tid":1200331,"uid":208046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc975104c027645484515d70838765a029c70441","tid":1200331,"uid":10895,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:43:13.000Z","msg":"美國國旗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:47:41.000Z","msg":"屌 點解第一下諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e373d2f97168ad3ddd5de71dbffa3bade57acd8c","tid":1200331,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:47:55.000Z","msg":"我是堅決反對你們玩國旗的，用愛國的心對抗林鄭月娥才是正路。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1200292\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1200292</a>"},{"pid":"732f8ef2344831da013edc9e84c07ab58a5216f1","tid":1200331,"uid":258144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,